    "7328503": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Sosi",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What does Sosi want to show us? Isn't this just one big stone tablet?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... did it get eroded? Paimon can't make out what's written on it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "The Khvarena Monument is a valuable artifact to the Order of Skeptics. It only appears this way because its fragments are lost."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "Engraved on the monument are the true names of every Pari and the first contract they formed with the Order of Skeptics."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "The immortality of the Pari is sustained by the Khvarena Monument. One who manages to collect all four fragments and causes the contract to reappear..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "...Will re-establish a contract with the Pari and obtain a power that rivals the gods."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sounds nice and all, but what does that have to do with us?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, we're not interested in obtaining the power of the gods."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "As for forming contracts with Pari... We're already friends with Sorush, so Paimon thinks there's no need for formalities like that!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "Who told you we were friends? Do mind your manners, Pale Floater."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Um, you do have a point. We'll be friends once Paimon returns the favor by coming up with an ugly nickname for you! Hehe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "#Hmph! Paimon's disrespectful behavior aside, I assume you're planning to task {NICKNAME} with collecting the monument's fragments?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "That's very observant of you, Lady Sorush. That is indeed my plan."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "Searching is quite a lowly task— Ahem, a task requiring adventure experience is better suited for professionals. And by that, I mean adventurers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "So you seek to form a new contract with us Pari and acquire a power that rivals the gods?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "Oh, how very interesting. A mere human, coveting a higher power... Could it be your inflated ego, or utter ignorance?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "How could I have such presumptuous thoughts...! I'm doing all this for the sake of research and bringing the historical truth to light."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "The Akademiya and the Order of Skeptics went separate ways due to a clash in our ideals, but our research has always emphasized history and heritage."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "I have never once coveted a higher power — the only thing I'm after is the contents of the inscription on the Khvarena Monument. It's all for the sake of research, I swear."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "The initial contract between us Skeptics and the Pari, and every single Pari's true name! Isn't that enough to pique your interest?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I gotta admit, I am a bit curious."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "I suppose that's no surprise, coming from an adventurer with Lady Sorush's recognition..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Not really. It's not like I can memorize everything..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "You're only interested in treasure, huh... Well, can't say I don't understand."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "Anyway, this is a formal commission. Please be assured that you will be well compensated by the Order of Skeptics."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, since it's a formal commission with compensation and all, maybe we should give it a go."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "Splendid. Here are some clues regarding the locations of the monument's fragments... I trust that you're already familiar with clues like these as experienced adventurers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "Oh, and one more thing. I have indeed sighted suspicious individuals who covet the power of gods. They seem to have come all the way from the snowy lands..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "I've seen them sneaking around the Khvarena Monument, and it's clear that they're up to no good. They've even started setting up camp nearby..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "I'm sure you wouldn't put up with these outlanders acting as they please on our land, Lady Sorush?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sounds like the Fatui... We just gotta chase them away, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "Yes, that's right, go teach them a lesson. They've set up three separate camps — I'll mark them on your map later."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "There's a commanding officer among them that watches over the whole situation. Perhaps defeating him would teach these outlanders to abide by our rules."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "Okay, enough talk. I leave the matter in your hands while I stay here and continue reading up on relevant documents. With Lady Sorush accompanying you, I'm sure everything will go smoothly."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
