    "7328505": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Sosi",
        "Step": "Now that you've completed both of Sosi's commissions, it's time to give her the monument fragments you found.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "It seems that you've found all four monument fragments. About the Fatui that covet the power of the gods, especially their commanding officer..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He said some strange things."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And we couldn't talk any sense into him at all!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He was very polite."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, but it felt really weird!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "Worry not. My Yasnapati has already taught them the lesson they deserve."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "Ohh! Thank you for informing me, Lady Sorush. That puts my mind at ease."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "According to the records, as long as we return the four fragments to their original places, the inscription on the Khvarena Monument will reappear."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "I'll place the honor of returning the fragments in our esteemed Yasnapati's hands, then. I'm sure that would suit your preference too, Lady Sorush."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7328513": {
        "Desc": "Place the monument fragments",
        "Step": "Perhaps returning all fragments to their place will allow you to decipher the inscriptions engraved on the Khvarena Monument...",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "Lady Sorush, and you two... You..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Never mind that for now! You Skeptics... how could you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "Us Skeptics? You might want to re-organize your thoughts before speaking up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "You tell Sosi in detail about what Nasejuna had done..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "Is that so... But the incident seems completely arbitrary. His actions have undoubtedly violated the Order of Skeptics' true purpose, so one shouldn't generalize that to the whole order."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But isn't he the uh, Vijnanapati? Are you really gonna let this slide?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "Let's put his nonconforming deeds aside for now. There's something of higher importance I need your opinion on... and it has something to do with Lady Sorush."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well then... Since it has to do with Sorush, Paimon supposes we'll hear you out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "Wonderful! Please, come with me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is it something you can't say here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sosi",
                    "T": "No, it's just that some things are easier to understand after you've seen them yourselves."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
